original_title: Systema Naturae - or, a Metaphoric Masturbation About Man's Magic on Mastering
overview: Per Berg (Peter Wahlbeck) runs a cultural magazine about life and death in this meta-story and existential exposé of humanity’s relationship to animals, where laughs quickly get stuck in your throat.
title: Systema Naturae - or, a Metaphoric Masturbation About Man's Magic on Mastering
